{"tid":1948321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"去完大X樂先知個禁令流架","createTime":"2020-03-29T02:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T03:08:44.000Z","uid":47517,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9e4f405466699388e9314a916586ae938e4e82ab","tid":1948321,"uid":47517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:43:35.000Z","msg":"今朝去大X樂食早餐, 都諗住冇位外賣架啦<br />\n入餐廳之前就量體溫, 探個頭都34度, 屌你老母我發冷呀? 我叫阿姐探多次都係一樣, 叫我咪撚煩入去買野啦, 極度懷疑量體溫係做假, 做到發燒比你過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入到大X樂之後見到好多位封左, 其他位又坐哂人, 咁唯有外賣啦<br />\n等外賣期間見到張4人枱對住坐, 睇睇下其中一個走左, 另一個就拎住餐坐落去, 屌你老母原來可以俾唔識既人塔枱架?咁其他封位都可以照坐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後拎到外賣啦啦聲走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n總括黎講, 禁令流架, 職員唔會特登要你離開, 反正食完就走, 聽日就會有人挑戰坐封位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"275d095abb414b2320f3330234cfa39a4d98f2d3","tid":1948321,"uid":213877,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:44:09.000Z","msg":"仲去大家樂食早餐，屌你老母"},{"pid":"3579b39414150b8e6fe5583f18e8bde315864020","tid":1948321,"uid":2676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:44:46.000Z","msg":"支持藍店既垃圾"},{"pid":"1a00ae61db9b9cba669a5777738a93758fb988a6","tid":1948321,"uid":47517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"275d095abb414b2320f3330234cfa39a4d98f2d3","tid":1948321,"uid":213877,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:44:09.000Z","msg":"仲去大家樂食早餐，屌你老母"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T02:46:40.000Z","msg":"窮撚住公屋果區得呢間簡咋, 一係吉野家囉"},{"pid":"a01a46256f201ebf58a0b317f8918b032b0ea1c7","tid":1948321,"uid":69159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1a00ae61db9b9cba669a5777738a93758fb988a6","tid":1948321,"uid":47517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"275d095abb414b2320f3330234cfa39a4d98f2d3","tid":1948321,"uid":213877,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"202